Package: drawsf
Type: Package
Title: Interactively draw 'sf' geometries
Version: 0.1.0
Description: Draw shapes, lines, and points in an interactive 'shiny' app
    and return their geometries as 'sf' objects. Simple wrapper to facilitate
    manually building geometries and boundary boxes.
